[normal]QAA
[normal])
[normal] benchmark statement in 
[normal]f
[normal]orensic science
[normal]. 
[normal]This recognises forensic science as a subject in its own right, has science at its core and incorporates the unique nature of forensic science including the interpretation, evaluation and presentation of evidence. Any University now wishing to teach forensic science must meet this QAA benchmark.
[normal]1.4.2 Following the Home Office Review into research and development in forensic science 
